item.title: Talks: Episerver Content Providers & Lightening Talk
item.description: On the 23rd of March, I had the opportunity to present at the Episerver meetup in Redweb’s London offices. I ended up giving two talks: Episerver Content Providers & a 5 minute lightening talk.
